Requirement Summary
The objective of this assignment is to develop a TV series management application for a new streaming company. The application must provide a user-friendly menu that allows users to capture, search, update, delete, and print reports of TV series. The application will utilize a Series class to manage the series data, which includes attributes such as seriesId, seriesName, seriesAge, and seriesNumberOfEpisodes. Additionally, the application must handle user input validation and exceptions effectively.

